             <p class="intro">Earning the coveted CES Innovation Awards Honoree title provides engaging benefits:</p>

<ul>
	<li>
	<p>Innovation Awards Honoree logo to include on your product packaging and advertising materials.</p>
	</li>
	<li>
	<p>The opportunity to display your product in the Innovation Awards Showcase at CES, one of the most popular destinations on the show floor (for official CES exhibitors only).&nbsp;</p>
	</li>
	<li>
	<p>The opportunity to be featured on the live radio broadcast of &quot;Into Tomorrow&quot; with Dave Graveline. This nationally syndicated consumer electronics radio program features interviews with CEOs, presidents and senior executives from the hottest companies exhibiting at CES live from the show floor.</p>
	</li>
	<li>
	<p>Innovation Awards Honoree trophy to display in your exhibit at CES and in your company&#39;s trophy case.</p>
	</li>
	<li>
	<p>Industry-wide recognition and media attention through a CTA press release announcing the honorees.</p>
	</li>
	<li>Listing in the January/February issue of&nbsp;<em><a href="https://www.cta.tech/News/i3.aspx" target="_blank">It Is Innovation </a></em><a href="https://www.cta.tech/News/i3.aspx" target="_blank">(</a><em><a href="https://www.cta.tech/News/i3.aspx" target="_blank">i3</a></em><a href="https://www.cta.tech/News/i3.aspx" target="_blank">)</a><em>,&nbsp;</em>CTA&rsquo;s flagship publication distributed to more than 51,000 and bonus distribution at CES 2018 (for official CES Exhibitors only).</li>
	<li>
	<p>Exposure on the official CES website.</p>
	</li>
	<li>
	<p>Substantial discounts on advertising opportunities in CTA&#39;s&nbsp;<a href="https://www.cta.tech/News/i3.aspx" target="_blank"><em>It Is Innovation</em> (<em>i3</em>)&nbsp;magazine</a>.</p>
	</li>
	<li>The opportunity to display your product at additional CTA events throughout the year, including CES Unveiled New York and CES Unveiled Las Vegas.</li>
</ul>
